{"build_type":"library","description":"Launcher wrapper whose whole body is one real launch_worker_binary (tail-chain) of the generic capability-tool worker. The MCP tools/call dispatch calls this so the tool runs on a name-linked, crash-captured worker attached to the launch tree up to the root, instead of a hand-spawned floating worker.","module_name":"execute-capability-worker-spawning-launcher","package_name":"execute-capability-worker-spawning-launcher","function_definitions":{"execute-capability-worker-spawning-launcher":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"input","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"launch_worker_binary","target_binary":"run-capability-tool-from-request-as-worker","cycle_type":"tail-chain","input":"input"}]}}}